@ClassVersion(sourceVersion="$Id: UMLConnector.java 820 2020-12-29 20:34:22Z tquadrat $") @API(status=INTERNAL, since="0.0.5") public final class UMLConnector extends org.tquadrat.foundation.svg.SVGElementAdapter
The representation of the lines that connects the type elements in a UML diagram.

Instances of this class are used as if they are an instance of SVGPath.
Author:
